ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectReciprocal Provision of Supplies and Services between the Canadian Armed Forces and the Self-Defence Forces of Japan ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the GOVERNMENT OF JAPAN concerning the RECIPROCAL PROVISION OF SUPPLIES AND SERVICES BETWEEN THE CANADIAN ARMED FORCES and the SELF-DEFENCE FORCES OF JAPAN.
